node.text: @miss.fi.t u can support Chef bunny Seow n order seafood too!

Thanks to the very fresh tiger prawns from @kfreshfishery , #chefbunnyseow whipped out a very yummy garlic steamed prawns! She added some wine and the chap was sooooo good! Order now from @kfreshfishery and quote <<chefbunnyseow>> to get a free squid! No min purchase required! Order above $88 and get additional 500g of prawns!!
